{"tid":1394891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"縱火犯法，但盂蘭節燒街衣係合法架","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T04:50:04.000Z","uid":293077,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2436b7670ed164abd7f937405541fb9e82649d4a","tid":1394891,"uid":293077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:37:08.000Z","msg":"又到七月十四盂蘭節，咁多位孝子賢孫準備好燒嘢比先人未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港的《空氣污染管制(露天焚燒)規例》，明文禁止多項露天焚燒活動，惟按風俗、宗教儀式、節日或慶典上，為先人、神靈獻祭而燃燒香燭冥鏹、祭品或供奉，則屬豁免之一，故<span style=\"color: red;\">一般市民在盂蘭節作路祭不屬違法。</span>"},{"pid":"50aec6902b7de15b978238a1b1fdea1c6c73ff5b","tid":1394891,"uid":193565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:40:44.000Z","msg":"去中銀大廈燒"},{"pid":"7dc03094d086a311182a4650dff166fc267c5f8c","tid":1394891,"uid":293077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e3cf40b3da0946558e0037fa04bc08559173c1","tid":1394891,"uid":293077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:39:29.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"b07654d427e940ee5f0113a8a44e7cc7c6a6ed45","tid":1394891,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15528b26954c939a34b12e53346b2a7ab335e3d3","tid":1394891,"uid":209620,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />燒黨旗比以故領導人係愛國主義"},{"pid":"e844fb21fe89469ae400f0d068d96b91e09c9e3f","tid":1394891,"uid":89229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:42:19.000Z","msg":"推呀屌！"},{"pid":"f93d1e5765a7375e6e